  "body": "**Describe the bug**\r\nDuring testing on goerli testnet I've restarted Nethermind node and changed config in the meantime. After running run command, exceptions started appearing:\r\n\r\n```\r\n2022-08-24 15:20:52.1832|Invalid best state calculation: processed:7463862|state:7463862|block:7463850|header:7463850|chain difficulty:10790000|peer block:7463905|peer total difficulty:10790000\r\n2022-08-24 15:20:52.1832|Sync mode update failed System.ComponentModel.InvalidAsynchronousStateException: Invalid best state calculation: processed:7463862|state:\r\n7463862|block:7463850|header:7463850|chain difficulty:10790000|peer block:7463905|peer total difficulty:10790000\r\n   at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.VerifySnapshot(Snapshot best) in C:\\repos\\nethermind\\src\\Nethermind\\Nethermind.Synchronization\\ParallelSync\\MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 653\r\n   at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.TakeSnapshot(UInt256& peerDifficulty, Int64 peerBlock, Boolean inBeaconControl) in C:\\repos\\nethermind\\src\\Nethermind\\Nethermind.Synchronization\\ParallelSync\\MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 627\r\n   at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.Update() in C:\\repos\\nethermind\\src\\Nethermind\\Nethermind.Synchronization\\ParallelSync\\MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 174\r\n   at Nethermind.Synchronization.ParallelSync.MultiSyncModeSelector.StartAsync(CancellationToken cancellationToken) in C:\\repos\\nethermind\\src\\Nethermind\\Nethermind.Synchronization\\ParallelSync\\MultiSyncModeSelector.cs:line 129\r\n```\r\n\r\n**To Reproduce**\r\nThis was one time exception - after following restart everything came back to normal.\r\n\r\n**Desktop (please complete the following information):**\r\n - OS: Windows11\r\n\r\n**Additional context**\r\nLogs attached\r\n",
